com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.regression

Class Regression

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.regression.Regression

  • public class Regression
extends java.lang.Object

    Bean object for rebind module regression records. Intended to be serialized/deserialized by Jackson into/from JSON.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Calvin Goodrich
